WEBVTT

00:00:27.832 --> 00:00:31.832
and usually say the wrong thing
at the wrong time.

00:00:31.856 --> 00:00:36.354
Some people think that autistic people
are socially awkward

00:00:36.378 --> 00:00:38.417
and lack humor and empathy.

00:00:39.679 --> 00:00:43.060
Now if you agree with what I just said,

00:00:43.084 --> 00:00:44.498
I'm sorry to tell you,

00:00:44.522 --> 00:00:48.307
but you do not have
the right impression of autism.

00:00:48.934 --> 00:00:50.084
How do I know?

00:00:50.744 --> 00:00:53.593
Because I have autism.

00:00:54.323 --> 00:00:59.437
I do have my own obsessions
with things like electronics

00:00:59.461 --> 00:01:01.736
and public transit,